---
import BaseLayout from '../layouts/BaseLayout.astro';
---

<BaseLayout
  title="About Us - Crocheted Animals"
  description="Learn about our passion for creating handcrafted crocheted animals. Each piece is made with love and premium materials."
>
  <section class="py-16 md:py-24">
    <div class="container mx-auto px-4">
      <div class="max-w-4xl mx-auto">
        <!-- Header -->
        <div class="text-center mb-12">
          <h1 class="font-serif text-4xl md:text-5xl lg:text-6xl font-bold text-stone-800 mb-4">
            About Us
          </h1>
          <p class="text-lg text-stone-600">
            Crafting joy, one stitch at a time
          </p>
        </div>

        <!-- Story -->
        <div class="prose prose-lg prose-stone max-w-none">
          <div class="bg-white rounded-lg shadow-lg p-8 mb-8">
            <h2 class="font-serif text-3xl font-bold text-stone-800 mb-4">Our Story</h2>
            <p class="text-stone-600 leading-relaxed mb-4">
              What started as a simple hobby has blossomed into a passionate endeavor to bring joy
              through handcrafted crocheted companions. Each piece we create carries the warmth of
              countless hours of careful work and the love that goes into every single stitch.
            </p>
            <p class="text-stone-600 leading-relaxed mb-4">
              We believe that handmade items carry a special magicâ€”they're more than just objects,
              they're treasured companions that become part of your family's story. Whether it's a
              cuddly bear for a child's first birthday, a custom fox for a woodland-themed nursery,
              or a unique gift that shows someone you truly care, our creations are made to be
              cherished for years to come.
            </p>
            <p class="text-stone-600 leading-relaxed">
              Every animal that leaves our hands is a labor of love, crafted with premium materials
              and meticulous attention to detail. We take pride in our work and stand behind the
              quality of each piece.
            </p>
          </div>

          <!-- Our Process -->
          <div class="bg-stone-50 rounded-lg p-8 mb-8">
            <h2 class="font-serif text-3xl font-bold text-stone-800 mb-6">Our Crafting Process</h2>
            <div class="space-y-6">
              <div class="flex gap-4">
                <div class="flex-shrink-0 w-8 h-8 bg-rose-600 text-white rounded-full flex items-center justify-center font-bold">
                  1
                </div>
                <div>
                  <h3 class="font-bold text-lg text-stone-800 mb-2">Material Selection</h3>
                  <p class="text-stone-600">
                    We carefully select premium yarns and hypoallergenic fillings, ensuring each
                    material meets our quality standards and is safe for all ages.
                  </p>
                </div>
              </div>

              <div class="flex gap-4">
                <div class="flex-shrink-0 w-8 h-8 bg-rose-600 text-white rounded-full flex items-center justify-center font-bold">
                  2
                </div>
                <div>
                  <h3 class="font-bold text-lg text-stone-800 mb-2">Handcrafting</h3>
                  <p class="text-stone-600">
                    Each piece is crocheted by hand, with careful attention to tension, shaping, and
                    detail. Most items take 8-15 hours to complete.
                  </p>
                </div>
              </div>

              <div class="flex gap-4">
                <div class="flex-shrink-0 w-8 h-8 bg-rose-600 text-white rounded-full flex items-center justify-center font-bold">
                  3
                </div>
                <div>
                  <h3 class="font-bold text-lg text-stone-800 mb-2">Quality Check</h3>
                  <p class="text-stone-600">
                    Before shipping, every item undergoes a thorough quality inspection to ensure
                    it meets our standards and is securely constructed.
                  </p>
                </div>
              </div>

              <div class="flex gap-4">
                <div class="flex-shrink-0 w-8 h-8 bg-rose-600 text-white rounded-full flex items-center justify-center font-bold">
                  4
                </div>
                <div>
                  <h3 class="font-bold text-lg text-stone-800 mb-2">Careful Packaging</h3>
                  <p class="text-stone-600">
                    Your companion is lovingly packaged to ensure safe delivery, ready to bring
                    smiles upon arrival.
                  </p>
                </div>
              </div>
            </div>
          </div>

          <!-- Our Values -->
          <div class="bg-white rounded-lg shadow-lg p-8">
            <h2 class="font-serif text-3xl font-bold text-stone-800 mb-6">Our Values</h2>
            <div class="grid md:grid-cols-2 gap-6">
              <div>
                <h3 class="font-bold text-lg text-stone-800 mb-2">Quality First</h3>
                <p class="text-stone-600">
                  We never compromise on materials or craftsmanship. Every piece is made to last.
                </p>
              </div>
              <div>
                <h3 class="font-bold text-lg text-stone-800 mb-2">Sustainable Practices</h3>
                <p class="text-stone-600">
                  We source eco-friendly materials when possible and minimize waste in our process.
                </p>
              </div>
              <div>
                <h3 class="font-bold text-lg text-stone-800 mb-2">Customer Care</h3>
                <p class="text-stone-600">
                  Your satisfaction matters. We're here to ensure your experience is wonderful from
                  start to finish.
                </p>
              </div>
              <div>
                <h3 class="font-bold text-lg text-stone-800 mb-2">Creative Joy</h3>
                <p class="text-stone-600">
                  We love what we do, and it shows in every stitch. Each creation brings us joy,
                  and we hope it brings you joy too.
                </p>
              </div>
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>

        <!-- CTA -->
        <div class="mt-12 text-center">
          <p class="text-lg text-stone-600 mb-6">
            Ready to welcome a new companion into your home?
          </p>
          <div class="flex flex-col sm:flex-row gap-4 justify-center">
            <a
              href="/gallery"
              class="inline-block bg-rose-600 text-white px-8 py-4 rounded-lg font-semibold hover:bg-rose-700 transition-colors shadow-lg"
            >
              Browse Gallery
            </a>
            <a
              href="/custom-order"
              class="inline-block bg-white text-rose-600 border-2 border-rose-600 px-8 py-4 rounded-lg font-semibold hover:bg-stone-50 transition-colors"
            >
              Request Custom Order
            </a>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>
</BaseLayout>
